author: mturk
msg: Fix cache by removing reuse flag on reset endpoint.
Reset endpoint only when it will be stored in the cache. In case the
endpoit can not be stored in the cache it will be closed anyhow.

author: mturk
msg: Search for domain types 3 and 4 only if the worker has local workers
defined. They'll return null worker if not defined in any case.

author: mturk
msg: Add setter and getter for default cache size.
It is implemented on Apache2 for now, and will set default cache size
acording to number of thread per child
